Package: remoteclient
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED@
Depends: openssh-client, ssvnc | tigervnc-viewer, libicu76 | libicu74 | libicu73 | libicu72, libx11-6, libice6, libsm6, libfontconfig1, libglib2.0-0
Maintainer: Coimbra ITS <rviktor@gmail.com>
Description: RemoteAppClient operator console (Linux)
 Viewer-only operator console for RemoteAppClient: sign in, list managed
 devices, and open a VNC session through the bastion tunnel. No local agent
 is required - it mints a short-lived operator SSH certificate on sign-in.
